{"tid":995171,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人去過尾瀨之原","createTime":"2019-01-25T08:51:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T07:26:03.000Z","uid":76514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"96e8aa6df66bbbb858921b321139cce6767ce987","tid":995171,"uid":76514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T08:51:31.000Z","msg":"6月打算兩個人去東京尾瀨之原 有幾個問題想問<br />\n由於體力唔太好 幾乎0行山經驗 所以唔打算行晒全程(鳩待峠-&gt;大清水)<br />\n上網睇到三個初心者路線 有無人行過 可唔可以比啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kiEk1B3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkiEk1B3.png&h=c5829f31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1)呢個路線最短 佢話4個鐘行完 但會唔會無乜野睇?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q9J9UXv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq9J9UXv.png&h=aa54154f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2)呢個行程大概6個鐘 如果10點開始行會唔會太晏?<br />\n同埋相比起第3個路線會唔會睇少好多野?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AHUAQwa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAHUAQwa.png&h=7e50e0fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3)呢個路線就喺東電小屋住一晚 有無人住過?覺得點?<br />\n值唔值得行埋呢段路?<br />\n<br />\n另外就係想問吓你哋啲行李點處理?<br />\n因為有打算去那須玩同住一晚 那須附近有無地方可以寄存行李?<br />\n定係放啲行李喺東京都內 再揹背囊去那須同尾瀨好啲?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2241b110fc226682171e13d539d8821742f346c7","tid":995171,"uid":76514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T09:27:53.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3c39f29a69765b3a33283623800c3b8025c94f","tid":995171,"uid":76514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T12:59:56.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93665050ee9d6bccaee915477f1dd5798d342543","tid":995171,"uid":76514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T14:51:56.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de4e338a2c88567e731e7797b2c05e4bc4ca01f3","tid":995171,"uid":229608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T15:33:50.000Z","msg":"你確定係「東京尾瀬」？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw點解去尾瀬但要住東京？"},{"pid":"b7684a50a7a806614a2cf55f9eeb93e69ba8cd2c","tid":995171,"uid":76514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de4e338a2c88567e731e7797b2c05e4bc4ca01f3","tid":995171,"uid":229608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T15:33:50.000Z","msg":"你確定係「東京尾瀬」？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw點解去尾瀬但要住東京？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T15:53:09.000Z","msg":"講得唔清楚唔好意思 我地主要係東京都內同近郊玩<br />\n但因為尾瀨好似好靚 所以有啲遠都想去睇下<br />\n群馬嗰邊啲景點無咩興趣 所以唔係好想喺嗰邊訓一晚<br />\n所以諗緊有無可能東京去尾瀨即日來回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b39aa3d75feaaca95e6322cc3f2d2a35ba728319","tid":995171,"uid":229608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:25:01.000Z","msg":"勸告:不好即日來回。認真。<br />\n<br />\n另外，群馬實左太多正地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a3cfee5e4cf79ba0fe22438871371a5a89c017","tid":995171,"uid":229608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:26:40.000Z","msg":"尾瀬堅係好靚<br />\n<br />\n但你咁樣去揾來搞，留在東京玩較好"},{"pid":"f01a72ddc6e89f3ba0d06c97835de42f51df875c","tid":995171,"uid":76514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4a3cfee5e4cf79ba0fe22438871371a5a89c017","tid":995171,"uid":229608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:26:40.000Z","msg":"尾瀬堅係好靚<br />\n<br />\n但你咁樣去揾來搞，留在東京玩較好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:43:05.000Z","msg":"你嗰時係喺山上面小屋住一晚？"},{"pid":"baf817b67ec3c655da2c88cf57ae3bffd29d5cba